Product Marketing Context
Last updated: May 22, 2026

Product Overview
One-liner: India's first AI-powered broiler price intelligence platform for commercial poultry farmers.

What it does: Predicts broiler prices 7 days ahead with 95%+ accuracy using AI models trained on 47 public data sources, delivering daily sell/hold signals via WhatsApp at 6:30 AM.

Product category: Agricultural AI / Price Intelligence / Farm Decision Support

Product type: SaaS (B2B)

Business model: Monthly/annual subscription tiers (PulseFarm ₹2,000/mo, PulsePro ₹8,000/mo, PulseIntel custom for enterprise), with API licensing for enterprise customers.

Target Audience
Target companies: Commercial poultry farms with 10,000+ birds in India (currently focused on Gorakhpur belt: Gorakhpur, Deoria, Kushinagar, Basti, Maharajganj)

Decision-makers: Farm owners, farm managers, business decision-makers

Primary use case: Determining optimal timing to sell broiler flocks to maximize profit and avoid timing losses

Jobs to be done:

Know exactly when to sell to maximize profit (timing optimization)
Avoid ₹50,000–₹1,50,000 losses per batch from bad timing decisions
Get early warnings about disease outbreaks (HPAI) that could cause transport blocks
Plan feed schedules and transport bookings aligned with optimal sell windows
Use cases:

Daily sell/hold decision making for flock sales
7-day forward planning for feed and logistics
Disease risk mitigation (48-hour advance alerts)
Batch profit calculation and ROI tracking
